## ⚠️ **Code Quality Issues**

### 1. E2E Test Code Duplication (CRITICAL)

**SonarQube reports 28.7% duplication** (threshold: 3%). The primary issue is in `e2e/component-snapshots.spec.ts`.

**Problem:** Lines 13-337 repeat this pattern ~15 times:
```typescript
await page.goto('/');
await page.waitForTimeout(3000);
const santaButton = page.getByRole('button', { name: /MECHA-SANTA/ });
await santaButton.click();
await page.getByRole('button', { name: /COMMENCE OPERATION/i }).click();
await page.waitForTimeout(5000);
```

**Solution:** Extract to shared helper (already exists in `visual-regression.spec.ts:43-70`):

```typescript
// Create e2e/helpers.ts
export async function startGame(page: Page, characterName: RegExp | string) {
  await expect(page.getByText('INITIALIZING SYSTEMS')).not.toBeVisible({ timeout: 40000 });

  const charButton = page.getByRole('button', { name: characterName });
  await charButton.waitFor({ state: 'visible', timeout: 30000 });
  await page.waitForSelector('.overlay, .modal, .loading', { state: 'hidden', timeout: 5000 }).catch(() => {});

  await charButton.click({ force: true, timeout: 15000 });

  const commenceBtn = page.locator('[data-testid="mission-start-button"]').or(
    page.getByRole('button', { name: /COMMENCE OPERATION/i })
  );
  await commenceBtn.waitFor({ state: 'visible', timeout: 30000 });
  await commenceBtn.click({ force: true, timeout: 30000 });

  await expect(page.getByText('SCORE')).toBeVisible({ timeout: 30000 });
}

export async function disableAnimations(page: Page) {
  await page.addStyleTag({
    content: `
      *, *::before, *::after {
        animation-duration: 0s !important;
        transition-duration: 0s !important;
        animation-play-state: paused !important;
      }
    `
  });
}
```

**Impact:** This would reduce duplication from 28.7% to well below 3%, unblocking the SonarQube quality gate.

### 2. Magic Number Seeds

**Concern:** The seed values `124631605` and `12345` lack documentation.

**Recommendation:**
```typescript
// src/constants/testing.ts (or similar)
/**
 * Fixed seed for E2E visual regression testing.
 * DO NOT CHANGE: Changing this will invalidate all existing baseline screenshots.
 */
export const E2E_VISUAL_SEED = 124631605;

/**
 * Default gameplay seed for gameStore initial state.
 */
export const DEFAULT_GAMEPLAY_SEED = 12345;
```

Then import and use these named constants instead of magic numbers.

